description._content: Catalog #: 09_01849 Title: John Scott Hartje Special Collection Photo Additional Information: John Scott Hartje in military uniform in the snow building a snowball, 1944. Handwritten inscription ""From Scott to Uncle Al, Aunt Martha"", John Scott Hartje (b. 1922) served as a US Air Force pilot throughout World War II, mainly in the Pacific.
